<plot>This short showcases the work of the cameramen who filmed the battles of WWI and early WWII. We also get to see the faces of many of the men who took the pictures. This includes director 'D.W. Griffith' (qv), who shot newsreels in the trenches of WWI.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?091580</url></doc>
